{"tid":409164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 8料水位$300僅早上有得炒","createTime":"2017-09-21T23:55:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T02:26:06.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a82436cf236985c9b261670e2796ef403d36f28","tid":409164,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T23:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/TRnVa4A9fwCbLfDbFaSf0w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/skypost/22JHC001__20170922_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FTRnVa4A9fwCbLfDbFaSf0w--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fskypost%2F22JHC001__20170922_L.jpg&h=f17df3c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先達商場手機店主普遍認為iPhone 8炒價不高。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n【晴報專訊】iPhone 8今日正式抵港，但炒價卻被「果農」看淡。先達廣場手機店預計僅早上時段「炒得起」，但收機價最多貴300元；至下午時段隨時要「蝕讓離場」。另有手機店透露客人是「坐8望X」，即打算先買iPhone 8備用，待iPhone X出即換新機。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果新機iPhone 8未推出前，先達商場「回收」報價已跌穿定價，一致被「果農」看淡。但先達「流動帝國」店長Alex指，iPhone 8在今早仍有承接，炒價或升200至300元，當中iPhone 8 Plus需求較高，但他提醒︰「新機下午陸續到場，因為貨多可能要蝕讓離場，如有機就要盡早放出。」Alex透露，早前接到近300張訂單，當中以非首發地區的外國客戶為主；因炒價難起，暫仍未決定是否派人外出收機。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>256GB iPhone 8 Plus需求最高</strong><br />\n<br />\n先達「數碼匯」負責人阿勇則指，早前接到約50張定訂單，以256GB的iPhone 8 Plus需求最高，但炒價僅多100元，「細機都未必收」。他坦言今次iPhone 8預訂遠遜於同系列手機，「iPhone 6s及iPhone 7推出首日，最少都有80至100張定單。」<br />\n<br />\n旺角先達廣場手機店「i世代」負責人姚進指，接到約50張定單，雖然炒價不被看好，但有部分人抱着「嘗鮮」心態落訂︰「始終iPhone X要11月才推出，有客人在『過渡期』會先出iPhone 8，待iPhone X推出即換機，明知蝕讓亦在所不惜。」<br />\n<br />\n記者︰脫芷晴<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/iphone-8-%E6%96%99%E6%B0%B4%E4%BD%8D-300-%E5%83%85%E6%97%A9%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%89%E5%BE%97%E7%82%92-225050655.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fiphone-8-%25E6%2596%2599%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E4%25BD%258D-300-%25E5%2583%2585%25E6%2597%25A9%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25BE%2597%25E7%2582%2592-225050655.html&d=gTn6uvpaPQ3FBLoDaMTMIzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=f2a519a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/iphone-8-%E6%96%99%E6%B0%B4%E4%BD%8D-300-%E5%83%85%E6%97%A9%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%89%E5%BE%97%E7%82%92-225050655.html</a>"},{"pid":"d22196356666b9e988e50478cd17ef1d478789d1","tid":409164,"uid":42487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T23:59:51.000Z","msg":"眼紅者..."},{"pid":"d1865fcd439899ddb1bc2837a54f8ddfdcd41b5f","tid":409164,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T00:03:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>眼紅者...</blockquote><br />\n勿入錯貨"},{"pid":"b80d8c832fead7afe82fa6c7e4b6541446876f06","tid":409164,"uid":139224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T00:07:03.000Z","msg":"記者：脫芷晴<br />\n<br />\n原來有呢個姓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87fe7e1390457128d8155cd04a010f93dd6283a1","tid":409164,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T00:23:34.000Z","msg":"ST狗自己冇得賺直情收都唔會收 唔好講到百幾二百水位就好似皇恩浩蕩咁款"},{"pid":"38ce7b46ab1953283512e5654a41913a73a8d67b","tid":409164,"uid":83062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T00:36:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ST狗自己冇得賺直情收都唔會收 唔好講到百幾二百水位就好似皇恩浩蕩咁款</blockquote><br />\n搞手無得賺"},{"pid":"6c42e9486a4718e1f64ae0b64f3b8a69a440e78e","tid":409164,"uid":3107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T00:43:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>ST狗自己冇得賺直情收都唔會收 唔好講到百幾二百水位就好似皇恩浩蕩咁款</blockquote><br />\n搞手無得賺</blockquote><br />\n只求打個和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f9fad7177250a08185a0532fdedeafae9e8799","tid":409164,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T00:47:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>ST狗自己冇得賺直情收都唔會收 唔好講到百幾二百水位就好似皇恩浩蕩咁款</blockquote><br />\n搞手無得賺</blockquo